title: Iggy & The Stooges - Back To The Noise (2003) [FLAC]
description:
Very nice compilation by the Stooges-specialized Revenge label: CD1 includes raw & rare studio recordings and Outtakes. CD2 is the well known 'Live at the Whiskey-a-Gogo' plus one bonus track. Not unusal for original Stooges recordings from the '70s: the audio quality varies...
